Sec. 21-55. General criteria for RHO uses listed as SR in Section 21-113.
(3)
Building size. The aggregate or maximum square footage for a building(s) used as
a RHO is based on the type of road frontage; lot acreage, excluding right of way;
and zoning district, subject to:
a.
Location on a parcel containing at least thirty-five (35) feet of state road
frontage.
